" alt-hjkl for moving around word-wrapped lines
nnoremap <M-h> gh
nnoremap <M-j> gj
nnoremap <M-k> gk
nnoremap <M-l> gl

" trying alternatives to Esc for exiting insert mode
inoremap kj <Esc>`^
inoremap lkj <Esc>`^:w<CR>
inoremap ;lkj <Esc>:wq<CR>

cmap <M-h> <Left>
cmap <M-j> <Down>
cmap <M-k> <Up>
cmap <M-l> <Right>
cmap <M-0> <Home>

imap <C-l> <C-O>:redr!<CR>
